{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act41side", "eventName": "輓歌燃燒殆盡", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "EA-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "燒燈者", "storyInfo": "愛布拉娜倒下，城中的紫火卻越燒越烈，拉芙希妮、涅梅絲、布莉吉，三個人各自行動起來……第二個故事到此結束。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小丘郡還有多遠？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還很遠呢。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐她……不會不知道的。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說實話，只有“雄辯家”那群人以為事情天衣無縫。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#6", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你還跟著我？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#6"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有得選，我也想在之前的營地裡舒舒服服地睡一覺啊。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "姐姐為什麼不阻止我？", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，說不定對你寄予厚望吧。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，她從來沒對我露出過那樣的眼神，在我同意當她的影子之後，她……", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿赫茉妮，我請求你……我請求你去告訴姐姐，我不想這樣。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_228_1#7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不想去小丘郡？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#7"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。還有，如果姐姐心情還不錯的話，我還想請你告訴她，從今以後，我——", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，沒有了。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，我就勉為其難替你傳這些話。“雄辯家”的眼線還蠻難躲的呢。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，謝謝，請你快點去吧……", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_228_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_226_weed_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……在姐姐……徹底厭倦之前。", "name": "“領袖”"}, "figure_art": "avg_226_weed_1#2"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "直到她抵達了小丘郡，阿赫茉妮才姍姍來遲。她明白這代表著什麼。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "然後，在那個夜晚，炮聲轟鳴，晶簇生長，她倒在小丘郡的街道上，血從她的腹部流出來。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她沒有覺得多害怕，反倒覺得如釋重負。她可以像無數普通人一樣死去。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "然後她看見不遠處的高樓上，那紫色的火焰來了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她這時才感到害怕。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她怕那火沒有看見自己，將自己和街道上的人一同變成傀儡。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她怕那火看見了自己，將受傷的自己帶回去，讓自己繼續當她的影子。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她和那火對視，試圖從中得到什麼關於自己未來的暗示，但她能看見的只有厭煩。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "她最害怕的事終於發生了。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g12_castlecorridor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "死去的紅龍躺在地上。"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "活著的紅龍身後，離群的守靈人剛剛明白一切。"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "59_g15_castlebalcony_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$eblana_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她騙了您。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，她沒有欺騙任何人。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她算準您不願讓整座城市的人為她陪葬，所以才自導自演了這麼一齣戲！", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她引誘您刺穿她的軀殼，而她自己則得以擺脫束縛，讓本來還沒那麼兇猛的紫火能在夏末節前夜把所有人燒光！", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#4$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她為什麼要為了一個平時從來不放在眼裡的節日……冒這樣的風險？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "紅龍，我也是身染紫火的活人，就連我也感受得到，死火正在我胸口燃燒，比任何時候都冰冷，冷得我馬上就要失去知覺！", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管她現在是在圖謀整個塔拉，還是她已經瘋了，只想拉著整座城的人跟她一起死，怎樣都好，這些根本就不重要！", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#4$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，塔拉已經是她的囊中之物，她也絕對沒有瘋，那她……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她——", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "涅梅絲，她的屍首還在嗎？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我去看看。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "300,0", "posto": "0,0", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離群守靈人的眉毛皺成一團。也許她這輩子還沒萌生過這麼大的惡意，自然也就沒下過這麼大的決心。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的屍首就在——", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的回答聲被熊熊的燃燒聲蓋了過去。"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管她究竟要做什麼，納斯爾紗還沒有燃盡，還火儀式仍然辦得下去……必須要辦下去。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我明白您的意思了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會將這個消息告訴城裡人。告訴他們，那條被他們奉若神明的邪惡的紅龍已經死去。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布莉吉呢？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經拜託她離開城市，去找守靈人了。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#7$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但你該怎麼告訴其他人愛布拉娜已經死了？", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拖棺。那條紅龍應得的。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#2$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然城裡連棺材都快不夠了，但她畢竟不是什麼死在街頭的無名小卒，她配得上一副。", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#8$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不願意？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#6$1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我只是第一次意識到，愛布拉娜究竟走在一條多麼醜陋的道路上。現在這條路正向我招手，而我……別無選擇。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#13$1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去吧，涅梅絲，我會為你爭取時間。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "爭取時間，您是說黑霧？", "name": "涅梅絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1692_1#10$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。如果黑霧看準了夏末節，非要進城來湊熱鬧，我會拖住它。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經等不及要向黑霧請教，該如何讓紅龍的火光歸於黑暗了。", "name": "高尚的紅龍"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$darkness_03_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“我已經等不及要向黑霧請教，該如何讓紅龍的火光歸於黑暗了。”", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照這樣的發展，鏡中人和紅龍的結局已經呼之欲出了。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chairbump", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而作家倏然起身。"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你到底是誰？你到底要做什麼？", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "補全您不願意講完的故事啊。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您不是覺得我是那種喜歡“拼湊真相”的傢伙嗎？我們離真相已經很近很近了。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了，我得走了——", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果您無論如何都不願意由自己來講出那個結局，那就還是由我來把故事補完，怎麼樣？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#4$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>忽然，不知是誰睜開雙眼，鏡中人嚇得鬆開了手，而忘乎所以的紅龍掉進了篝火中，火焰熊熊燃燒，鏡中人趁機躲回了鏡子裡。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>然而等到火勢漸小之後，紅龍的身影再也沒有出現，人們為找不到紅龍焦急不已。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "<i>鏡中人想去跟大家解釋原委，找到讓紅龍回來的方法，但沒有了紅龍，她已經無法從鏡子裡面出來了。</i>", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如何？", "name": "神秘的女性"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到您一直在瞥那邊的報刊欄了。報紙不一定只報導事實，先生。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作家瞟了一眼酒館門口。"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想像了一下自己拔腿跑出酒館的場景。很滑稽，滑稽到他自己差點笑出來。"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果報紙沒有“報導事實”，那他終於知道這個人是誰了。至於她為什麼來找自己，理由也很好猜。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，自己是無論如何都跑不掉的。"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但他同時也意識到一件事。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許，他真的可以找到某個如他所願的結局。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不管她到底是誰，只要還在聊故事，他們就是平等的。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他覺得剛才那股頹喪之意正在消退。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姐，我現在不管你是誰，也不管你到底要來做什麼，但故事就不該這麼寫。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只是給一個沒結尾的故事延續了一小段，結局仍然付之闕如。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#5$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我問你，你看見了……一條紅龍殺死另一條的場景？", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就和您看見英雄將紅龍的骨架拖上廣場一樣，“創作”，僅此而已。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那就對你的創作負責。鏡子裡的紅龍失手讓另一個自己在篝火中燒死，然後呢？人們做了什麼？躲回鏡子裡的紅龍呢？", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您呢？您就沒有什麼想法嗎？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作家久違地從口袋裡摸出鋼筆，又從桌上抓起一張紙牌。他想寫下點什麼，可惜鋼筆太久沒用，已經乾了。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還需要……一點時間。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，連得上，連得上……也許能連得上……", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連得上？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜您想說的，是您出版的最後一個故事？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作家的鋼筆在紙牌上狠狠劃過，終於有一絲墨水滲了出來。"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“願死亡將我們與一切傳奇相連”，這句西莫·威廉姆斯的話突然闖進了他的腦海。"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "西莫·威廉姆斯已經死了，而自己也許……真的能不揣冒昧地……與他書寫的傳奇相連。"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他想把這句詩在紙牌上寫下來，但鋼筆尖只在紙上留下了幾道斷裂到無法辨認的墨跡。"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許……", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_chairrub", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作家坐回椅子上，甚至比剛才坐得更直了一點。"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他突然感受到某種衝動，和他第一次聽見西莫·威廉姆斯的詩時類似的衝動。"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那讓他一路淪落至此，但他至今仍記得的，那種緊緊捏住他的胸腹，讓他迫不及待想歌唱、想呐喊——"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想創作的衝動。"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許你的確幫我解決了一些問題。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說過，我看見的、我相信的、我說出口的，彼此全都背道而馳。但拜你所賜，它們似乎終於有了一點融為一體的跡象。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那真是再好不過了。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，您可以開始講述第三個故事了嗎？", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然……當然。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不僅如此，我還需要你的協助，小姐。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在我停滯的時候，我需要你來講。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#2$1"}, {"id": 268, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我的故事，但也是你的。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從一開始就是你的。", "name": "作家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樂意效勞。", "name": "神秘的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1698_1#1$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_paper2", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作家的呼吸急促，臉上泛起激動的潮紅。鋼筆無論怎麼劃也無法正常寫字，他乾脆將那隻筆往桌子上一摔。"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，是啊。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些事情，他見得還不夠多嗎？"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又能怎麼樣呢？"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他是個作家，他馬上就要為自己的故事找到結局。"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}